<i>adverb</i>: 덧없이 [더덥씨] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>덧없이 [더덥씨]</dt><br>
<dd>1. fleetingly</dd><br>
<dd>시간이 너무 빨리 지나가서 허무하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In vain as time passes so fast.</dd><br>
<dd>2. in vain</dd><br>
<dd>삶이 보람이나 가치를 느낄 수 없이 헛되이.</dd><br>
<dd>The feeling that life is all in vain without any reward or value in it.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>